:::Atma/Psuedo/Wheeljack/Maximus Prime/Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky 
Lynx/Orion:::

::Psuedo's spark was pounding with joy at seeing his wife again::
Psuedo: Oh, we.. and then.. and-
Atma: What hes trying to say is, no we didnt die.  Our sparks were absorbed 
by that evil bot.  Hes dead now, and our sparks returned to our bodies.
::Psuedo runs up Technosis, embraces her, and holds her tight to him::
Psuedo: You cant write us off that easily.  What have you been doing all this 
time?
~~~~~
Wheeljack: Thats our goal.
::He gets the missles he needs and heads back and starts working on the 
modifications::
~~~~~
::Torca fires 2 charges at Greven::
~~~~~
::Ratchet fires 15 shots from each gun and 2 tusk missles at Demise::
~~~~~
::Sideswipe fires 25 shots and 2 missles at Demise::
~~~~~
::Sky Lynx fires 2 missles from each gun at Motormaster::
~~~~~
::Orion fires 2 missles at Motormaster::
~~~~~
::Maximus Prime fires 2 missles from each of his four guns at Killfest::

--part1_7a.104f07f8.27b623a3_boundary
